# Privacy Policy - Trip Lanka

**Last Updated: June 26, 2026**

## 1. Introduction

Trip Lanka we is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.

## 2. Information We Collect

### 2.1 Personal Information
- **Account Information**: When you create an account, we collect your name, email address, and role (user/admin)
- **Location Data**: We collect your approximate location to show nearby places and provide navigation features
- **Device Information**: We collect device type, operating system version, and unique device identifiers for analytics

### 2.2 Usage Data
- **App Usage**: We track which places you view, add to wishlist, or mark as visited
- **Login Activity**: We record when you log in to the app
- **Engagement Metrics**: We collect data on how you interact with the app to improve user experience

### 2.3 Permissions Required
- **Location**: To find nearby places and provide navigation 
- **Internet**: To load content and sync with our servers
- **Storage**: To cache images and data for offline access

## 3. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:
- Provide and improve our services
- Show personalized recommendations based on your location
- Enable navigation features
- Track user engagement for analytics
- Send important notifications about app updates
- Admin users can manage user accounts and view analytics

## 4. Data Storage and Security

- **Cloud Storage**: Your data is stored securely on Supabase cloud infrastructure
- **Local Storage**: Some data is cached on your device for offline access
- **Encryption**: We use industry-standard encryption to protect your data
- **Access Control**: Only authorized personnel can access user data

## 5. Data Sharing

We do **not** sell your personal information. We may share data with:
- **Service Providers**: Supabase (our cloud database provider) for data storage
- **Analytics**: Anonymous usage data for app improvement
- **Legal Requirements**: When required by law

## 6. Third-Party Services

Our app integrates with:
- **Supabase**: For authentication and database services
- **Google Maps**: For external navigation (opens in Google Maps app)
- **Google AdMob**: For displaying advertisements

## 7. Your Rights

You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Correct inaccurate data
- Delete your account and associated data
- Opt-out of location tracking
- Withdraw consent at any time

## 8. Children's Privacy

Our app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## 9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.

